race.comment: LIKE A BLAZE (6) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish second, beaten half a length, (24.48) at this track. One of the contenders. SMILING BEE (4) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at this track over 425m (24.43). Has a strong record from box 4, including two wins. Has the ability to give this a shake. HELLO COOPER (7) finds it hard to win. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing third (24.83) at this track. Form here sound including four wins. Will give a great sight again. ROCK SHOW (1) can sneak into the finish.
